song.title: Final Lap
song.info: The tune is inspired by Namco Ridge Racer 4 game on PlayStation. Tracked for futuristic racing game on PC called "Jet Jumper". I've tried to bring a "syntetic" feeling into this tune by using oldschool demoscenish solo in the middle part. Most samples from Apple Garage Band. Impulse Tracker realtime filters used a lot.
